"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲未搞清楚個現實<br />\n搞抗爭就係冇人權<br />\n唔好再諗埋啲屎橋諗住避"},{"pid":"335c9ebf6b8e3745448b71d36f65dc0abc94520c","tid":2008101,"uid":86774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T09:54:53.000Z","msg":"樂富街坊要小心：有幾十個黑衣惡人今日五點左右喺佛教醫院附近的食棧酒樓出沒，唔知有咩企圖。"},{"pid":"de4d050ce6175f31a060455176585490827c0663","tid":2008101,"uid":35699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"94a90a2d5e72cc183c7bf4d5bb3a16fa3943d8db","tid":2008101,"uid":40216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T18:58:40.000Z","msg":"所謂的「自警團」（じけいだん，英文的 Vigilante）是指由民間所組成的團體，出於自衛的需求、或是為了維持地方治安，集結組織的共同體；在治安敗壞、混亂或戰爭時期的社會較常出現，大型災害之後如日本1923年關東大地震，也有不少民間自警團在城鎮市區裡活動。<br />\n<br />\n關於自警團呢個概念，舊登係4年前已經討論過：<a href=\"https://forum.hkgolden.com/thread/6289745/page/1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforum.hkgolden.com%2Fthread%2F6289745%2Fpage%2F1&d=i%2FQ10njZfEvfzeNkfPb7d2yprV%2B6HEKZLwhfW4p%2FhGU%3D&h=de42ddde\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forum.hkgolden.com/thread/6289745/page/1</a><br />\n當時既構想：<br />\n- 2至3人一組在地區巡邏 （可以發展去到4-5人一組，但要係限聚令既範圍以内）<br />\n- 義務性質，唔收錢唔收禮<br />\n- 有罪案發生時，行使公民逮捕權將犯人逮捕，必要時使用合理武力遏止罪案<br />\n<br />\n當時舊登仔仍然相信警方會執法，所以認爲最後自警團都係要交犯比警察，但目前情況已經好唔同，自然需要臨陣應變<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n目前受支那病毒侵襲既日本亦有組織自警團執行&ldquo;民間戒嚴&rdquo;：<a href=\"https://global.udn.com/global_vision/story/8664/4548698\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fglobal.udn.com%2Fglobal_vision%2Fstory%2F8664%2F4548698&d=i%2FQ10njZfEvfzeNkfPb7d2yprV%2B6HEKZLwhfW4p%2FhGU%3D&h=f1e27ceb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://global.udn.com/global_vision/story/8664/4548698</a><br />\n<br />\n比起解散警隊，更加有效既做法係架空警隊，組織民間防衛力量，除左文宣之外亦可以將保衛範圍拓展去各個社區既黃店，除非有手足比狗咬，否則自警團需要避免同狗直接正面肢體衝突<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而樂富事件似乎就係一個唔錯既契機，而由今日立法會既衝突可以預見，未來支共只會更加明目張膽，無論係議會定法庭可以抗爭既空間只會日漸萎縮，所以自警團係未來只會越來越重要，而且越早組織越好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n認同<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n反對<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T10:09:19.000Z","msg":"黃絲：好暴力呀<br />\n<br />\n黃絲：乜撚對付魔鬼唔好將自己變成魔鬼"},{"pid":"e7105a7734b1bb61c832559c4eb9a131f88e666a","tid":2008101,"uid":354682,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T10:15:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7554934d856d14ffd8bf4716ea486fb7be35d96","tid":2008101,"uid":47475,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"45e3f452ec1fb01d3de8448d188a6227e146b5df","tid":2008101,"uid":40216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"46314213b7e70377683623cfecd8eeda5cc77d80","tid":2008101,"uid":59973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T02:36:05.000Z","msg":"民團會犯法，首先要諗點過骨，而家唔係5/60年代，個政府實唔會隻眼開隻眼閉"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T09:47:39.000Z","msg":"就算你係保安公司授權既保安，警察一樣可以告你非法集會，所以主要既困難唔係法律層面上面"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T10:22:02.000Z","msg":"同獨立一樣，係香港人嘅文化習慣同有冇呢個意識嘅問題。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45df5994bd1f1304173d95970bd33c8f022b7d5b","tid":2008101,"uid":8423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0deb7ba469aec70dbc7116b0d8f7958ebe06f2ae","tid":2008101,"uid":40216,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"afce719edf81ac1bc5a57946a709832e4f6d80b0","tid":2008101,"uid":8423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T02:33:27.000Z","msg":"可以成立公司或者類似同鄉會組織<br />\n然後地區組織自己組成自警團<br />\n然後必要時邀請當區區議員幫助<br />\n點睇"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T09:46:29.000Z","msg":"區議會授權組織自警團"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T10:36:02.000Z","msg":"正